# patches/series — ordered RAVEN patch series, applied by build/apply-patches.sh
# on top of the ungoogled tree (ungoogled's own series is applied by build/sync.sh).
#
# One patch path per line, RELATIVE TO patches/. Order = apply order.
#   core/1xx-*.patch         architecture: PRNG, keyed seed, descriptor (Plan 02)
#   fingerprint/{b0x,0xx}    rebased baseline 19 (Plan 01)  <-- fp-chromium 144 set
#   fingerprint/2xx-*.patch  new surfaces (Plan 03)
#
# Plan 01: fingerprint-chromium 144 fingerprint surface, rebased 144->150.
# Order mirrors fingerprint-chromium's own patches/series (bromite block first,
# then the 000-018 fingerprint block). fingerprint-chromium is ungoogled-based,
# so these were authored against ungoogled-144 and apply onto ungoogled-150 with
# `git apply --3way` (same base, milestone delta only).

# --- core block (Plan 02: PRNG/seed/descriptor architecture) ---
# 100 (lifted primitives + absl visibility) and 101 (Profile + platform/BUILD.gn)
# add new files / independent edits, so they apply first. 102 (plumbing) EXTENDS
# fingerprint/000's switch block, so it is ordered AFTER the fingerprint block (EOF).
